@startuml
title Diagrama de Implantacao Simplificado da Solucao

left to right direction

node "No cliente\nNavegador web\nHTML + CSS + JavaScript" as Cliente
node "No web\nVercel\nsite estatico" as Web
node "No backend\nSupabase\nAuth + PostgreSQL + Edge Functions" as Backend
cloud "Stripe" as Stripe
cloud "Mercado Pago" as MercadoPago
cloud "Resend / E-mail\ntransacional" as Email

Cliente --> Web : HTTPS
Web --> Backend : API / Auth
Backend --> Stripe : checkout / webhook
Backend --> MercadoPago : OAuth
Backend --> Email : envio de e-mail

@enduml
